ree Gaussian distribution (semicircle law),\nrespectively. We then further derive the CLTs for the linear spectral\nstatistics of the block correlation matrix under general setting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2022 10:28:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2022 02:44:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-09"}
