 that can be\nused to counteract other TTL effects. Altogether, our results provide key\nknowledge to minimise the total TTL coupling noise in experiments by design or\nrealignment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2022 15:23:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2022 21:35:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 4 Jan 2023 11:17:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-17"}
